title: The Empire Strikes Back Uncut (Official FAN MADE Full Movie)
description:
Watch the full version of The Empire Strikes Back Uncut, a FAN-MADE, shot-for-shot remake of the Star Wars classic!

This is a 720p HD MP4 video. It can also be viewed on YouTube or the official site StarWarsUncut.com
